{"tid":2044064,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"迫香港人攬明州事件上身的會員 聖哈利路亞小姐有問題","createTime":"2020-05-31T00:18:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-31T05:02:10.000Z","uid":26770,"like":32,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"e9f46276b134a900240a7db42de55faab8333f24","tid":2044064,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T00:18:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2043996/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2043996/page/1</a><br />\n條友#21開始不停9up唔攬上身就係不義<br />\n美國警暴已拉左警魔<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">而香港唔能夠停示威係因香港警魔強姦,水刑,開車撞人而無告</span><br />\n兩樣野性質完全不同<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1223187/page/1?post=2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1223187/page/1?post=2</a><br />\n屌9 示威者辱罵警嫂<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1214705/page/1?post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1214705/page/1?post=1</a><br />\n開post支持警魔唔好resign<br />\n可能怕老公比唔起家用?"},{"pid":"ba3c5fcc59f1f176757ee10a39f6f3792d176670","tid":2044064,"uid":143343,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T00:22:02.000Z","msg":"唔怪之得我一直覺得佢怪怪地"},{"pid":"87bd182bb3d0df069600184b019da44ceb944b46","tid":2044064,"uid":140538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T00:23:38.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbebc4beee6dc20c6882d821c4b5d967472b0083","tid":2044064,"uid":140538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T00:23:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f95d2a4da690c56d887e79600e08365f28b56d50","tid":2044064,"uid":26770,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ba3c5fcc59f1f176757ee10a39f6f3792d176670","tid":2044064,"uid":143343,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T00:22:02.000Z","msg":"唔怪之得我一直覺得佢怪怪地"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T00:24:31.000Z","msg":"一方面可能有警嫂同情示威者遭強姦<br />\n但好現實嫁狗都